Pull all the stuff

Usage: mwdev --pull-all --all
       mwdev --pull-all --skins
       mwdev --pull-all --extensions
       mwdev --pull-all --extensions --async 30

--all                           Run for all skins, extensions and core
--skins                         Run for all skins
--extensions                    Run for all extensions
--async <int>                   Pull things async, running the number of threads specified (default 25)
